# Incident Report: Administrator Group Modification

## Incident Summary

A user account was added to the local Administrators group. Changes to privileged groups are high-risk events and should always be reviewed.

---

## Incident Information

| Field | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Incident Name | Administrator Group Modification |
| Severity | High |
| Event ID | 4732 |
| Detection Source | Microsoft Sentinel |
| Data Source | Windows Security Logs |
| Affected Machine | SOC-WIN10-01 |
| Status | Investigated |

---

## Detection Logic

The analytics rule monitors Windows Security Event ID **4732**, which records when a user is added to a security-enabled local group.

---

