## Evidence Collected

- Modified group
- Added account
- Administrator performing the change
- Timestamp

---

## Investigation

The administrator group modification was intentionally performed for lab validation. In a production environment, unauthorized privilege escalation should be investigated immediately.

---

## MITRE ATT&CK Mapping

| Tactic | Technique | Technique ID |
|----------|-----------|--------------|
| Privilege Escalation | Account Manipulation | T1098 |

---

## Impact Assessment

Unauthorized administrator privileges may allow attackers to execute privileged commands, disable security controls, and establish persistence.

---

## Recommended Response

- Verify authorization for the group modification.
- Remove unauthorized members.
- Audit privileged account activity.
- Monitor subsequent administrative actions.

---

## Lessons Learned

Monitoring privileged group modifications helps detect privilege escalation before attackers gain full administrative control.
